      "author": "ryanravn",
      "description": "First release of the continued fork.\n\n## Highlights\n- **Encrypted repository support** (enc_version 2 and 4): passphrase prompt on repo selection and on Obsidian restart, never stored in plaintext.\n- **Manual sync**: \"Sync now\" button in settings and a \"Seafile: Sync now\" command (assignable to a hotkey).\n\n## Credits\nOriginal plugin by [@conql](https://github.com/conql). Continuation maintained by [@ryanravn](https://github.com/ryanravn).",
